  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Brand Ambassador",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking enthusiastic and motivated individuals to join our team as <strong>Brand Ambassadors</strong>. This role offers hands-on experience in <strong>face-to-face marketing, client engagement, and events-based campaigns</strong>, supported by structured training and mentorship.</p><p>You will represent client brands during events, engage customers, and support the execution of marketing campaigns. As you progress, you will be trained in team coordination, project management, and leadership skills, preparing you for future supervisory roles.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Conduct face-to-face marketing and promotional activities at events</p></li><li><p>Increase brand awareness and customer engagement for clients</p></li><li><p>Support planning and execution of marketing campaigns</p></li><li><p>Work with team members to achieve campaign objectives</p></li><li><p>Develop leadership skills by assisting in team and project management</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Willingness to learn and adapt in a dynamic environment</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated and responsible</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working in customer-facing roles</p></li><li><p>No prior experience required; training will be provided</p></li></ul><h3>Training & Development</h3><ul><li><p>Structured onboarding and continuous training programme</p></li><li><p>One-on-one mentorship from experienced leaders</p></li><li><p>Clear career progression into leadership and management roles</p></li></ul><h3>Benefits</h3><ul><li><p>Performance-based incentives</p></li><li><p>Local and overseas travel opportunities</p></li><li><p>Supportive and growth-focused work environment</p></li></ul><p>If you are looking for a long-term career in sales and marketing with leadership development, we welcome your application.</p>",
